title: Holiday Game Jam Announcement!
body:
Holiday Game Jam is Here!

Make a game by Thanksgiving at midnight for a chance to be featured! The winner of the Halloween Game Jam was FrigedRaccoon with Pumpkin Clicker! Don't miss your chance to be featured and make a game! (Try out the Construct Game Engine if you're unsure where to start!)

Rules

  • Make a game by Thanksgiving at midnight
  • Holiday themed (Any holiday in November-December)
  • Single-player

Submit your game here!
